{
  "stem": "4187.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they had to get out, because my grandfather was a great, great Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, his home, his country, his all that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so he-- he-- he was literally thrown out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because he was given-- well, offered a very high position in-- in his field, of course.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and he said, I have sworn to the Hungarian law not to the Yugoslav law.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they said, well then, goodbye.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they threw him out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had to go up to Budapest, then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so my mother and my aunt-- Aunt Vera, who is dead-- they-- they both went to university.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were virtually hungry for the university years, because there was no-- no one to-- you know, to-- to keep them while they were studying.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it was very hard times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's the main thing, they did it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that's-- that's-- that's the background.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "On my mother's-- or my-- sorry, about my-- my father, on my father's side, there was certainly no hint of any-- any religious Jewishness at all, nothing, nothing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My grandfather, as much as I remember him, I've never, ever heard him touch on the subject.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I-- I heard a lot of stories about my grandmother, because that was interesting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because her mother was a Russian aristocrat, actually.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she was a concert pianist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But she was-- she-- they wouldn't let her actually concertise, because that wasn't done.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But-- and-- and then she married an-- an Italian, who was also a doctor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they lived in the most incredible places in the world.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So that was a-- a fascinating story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I heard about that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I didn't hear much about my grandfather, because he was just a-- he was a veterinary surgeon.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
